<span id="fn_17"></span>[18](cc17010.htm#fr_17.md) <span
id="xi.xii-p11.1"></span>

<span id="xi.xii-p12"></span> The original word, <span
id="xi.xii-p12.1"></span>כסא, not only means a throne, but a seat; see
<span id="xi.xii-p12.2"></span>[1Sa
1:9](../../../bib/kjv/sa1001.htm#009.md)<span id="xi.xii-p12.2"></span>;
<span id="xi.xii-p12.3"></span>[1Sa
